    <summary>Drivers and software for Wacom pen products, including Wacom Tablet Properties and Wacom Desktop Center</summary>
    <description>
**This package is not official and is not affiliated with Wacom!**
This package installs drivers and supporting software for configuring Wacom hardware such as:

* Pen computers: Wacom MobileStudio Pro (DTH-W1320 and others), Wacom Cintiq Companion (DTH-1320)
* Pen displays: Wacom One Creative Pen Display (DTC133)
* Pen tablets: One by Wacom (CTL-471 and others), Intuos Pro (PTH-451 and others)
* Some accessoires: ExpressKey Remote (EKR-100)

You can see full list of compatible products in [release notes](https://cdn.wacom.com/u/productsupport/drivers/win/professional/releasenotes/Windows_6.3.42.html),
Smartpads, styluses and signature pads may require a separate driver.

Following are installed:

* Drivers for the table so it's recognized by other applications.
* Wacom Tablet Properties for configuring per-application pen-to-screen mapping, button actions, etc.
* Wacom Desktop Center for managing devices, backing up settings, etc.
  This application requires .NET 4.5, included as a dependency.
    </description>
